{"tid":2297752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★曾咀骨灰龕場位置偏僻，廢老不願入住！","createTime":"2020-11-23T13:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T13:54:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"efad2850a4594fecc94ccc33af135af0fd18b938","tid":2297752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"港府今年中開放屯門曾咀靈灰安置所內的約2.2萬個龕位供市民申請，但由於該骨灰龕場位置偏遠兼缺乏公共交通工具接駁，結果場內大量龕位無人問津。為免龕位被浪費，食環署宣布下月起全年接受市民申請曾咀靈灰安置所的龕位，每月推出約1700個，每月20日抽籤。<br />\n<br />\n食環署於今年5至6月，接受市民申請曾咀靈灰安置所，以及粉嶺和合石靈灰安置所第6期，合共提供的44,950個可續期骨灰龕位，當中曾咀提供的龕位佔了22,680個，但最終食環署只收到24,584份合資格申請，有多達45%龕位無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201123/bkn-20201123160604320-1123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201123%2Fbkn-20201123160604320-1123_00822_001.html&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=46cb2d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201123/bkn-20201123160604320-1123_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e25085dff3d52d030447aa337e1efd97094cafa","tid":2297752,"uid":85168,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"老貓住唔住？"},{"pid":"d17f14401f2f6559107559b0911ffc59d5c67464","tid":2297752,"uid":19454,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死左要返工咩？<br />\n<br />\n點解要交通方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8da2b012043fa3b9a67b5546e23240ab40c765",